<p>Because they cannot move orthogonally, the opposing unpromoted bishops can only reach half the squares of the board.</p>
<p><a name="Gold_general" id="Gold_general"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Shogi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Gold general">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Gold general</span></h3>
<p>A gold general can move one square orthogonally, or one square diagonally forward, giving it six possible destinations. It cannot move diagonally backward.</p>
