<p><a name="Silver_general" id="Silver_general"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Shogi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: Silver general">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Silver general</span></h3>
<p>A silver general can move one square diagonally or one square directly forward, giving it five possibilities.</p>
<table>
<tr>
<td>&#160;&#160;&#160;</td>
