<p><a name="Promoted_bishop" id="Promoted_bishop"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Shogi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: Promoted bishop">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Promoted bishop</span></h3>
<p>A promoted bishop ("dragon horse") may move as a bishop or as a king, but not as both on the same turn.</p>
